### CCR-010 — Auth Login with AUTH_PROFILE
###
### 검증:
### - 환경별 expires_in 차등 (dev=1h, staging/prod=2h, live=12h)
### - 응답에 expires_at (ISO 8601), auth_profile, refresh_expires_in 포함
### - AUTH_PROFILE 환경 플래그에 따라 token 만료 시간 변동

@host = http://localhost:8000

### 10.1 POST /api/v1/auth/login — dev 프로파일 (AUTH_PROFILE=dev)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin@ebs.test",
  "password": "test-password-1234"
}

# 예상 응답 (AUTH_PROFILE=dev 기동 시):
# 200 OK
# {
#   "access_token": "eyJhbGc...",
#   "refresh_token": "eyJhbGc...",
#   "expires_in": 3600,                          // 1h (dev)
#   "expires_at": "2026-04-10T15:34:56Z",
#   "auth_profile": "dev",
#   "refresh_expires_in": 86400                  // 24h (dev)
# }

### 10.2 POST /api/v1/auth/login — live 프로파일 (AUTH_PROFILE=live)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Test-Profile: live

{
  "username": "admin@ebs.test",
  "password": "test-password-1234"
}

# 예상 응답 (AUTH_PROFILE=live 기동 시):
# expires_in: 43200           // 12h (live, 방송용)
# refresh_expires_in: 604800  // 7d
# auth_profile: "live"

### 10.3 POST /api/v1/auth/refresh — 토큰 갱신
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "{{$dotenv REFRESH_TOKEN}}"
}

# 예상 응답: 새 access_token + expires_at 갱신
# WebSocket은 끊기지 않음 (BS-01-auth §5.3)

### 10.4 POST /api/v1/auth/refresh — 만료된 refresh token
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "eyJhbGc.expired..."
}

# 예상 응답:
# 401 Unauthorized
# { "error": "REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRED", "message": "..." }
